text: Kipsigak is a village near Kapsabet in Nandi County, Kenya. Administratively, Kipsigak is a location in Kilibwoni division of Nandi County.World Bank: Geographic Dimensions of Well-Being in Kenya Its local authority is Kapsabet municipality and constituency is Emgwen.Electoral Commission of Kenya: Registration centres by electoral area and constituency It is the birthplace of Kenyan runner Augustine Kiprono Choge. == References == Category:Populated places in Nandi County
title: Kipsigak
